{"type": "article", "id": 23607, "title": "彩色袜子包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174201rj2Pqi4KHGNxEf8M.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">捷克袜子品牌 FLASHTONES 的特色就是彩色的袜子，设计师在设计包装时想到了抽纸。他们利用回收后的硬纸板制作了方形盒子，正上方的大圆露出了袜子的颜色，也有衬托和表现颜色的作用。每只袜子装进一个小盒子里，鼓励随意搭配，穿不一样的袜子，这种活泼的做法正好配合了活泼的颜色。纸板上有金色的字母以标注品牌。<a href=\"http://www.flashtones.cz/\">这里是品牌链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174158JO9e06fsHzWqGFhc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174159KyGoHN4mk53Bbf1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174159cEVN1JGX8b9skjur.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174200RXsjwHC1tluyieJ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174200pdVkDtF3HaeQu5fq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}